<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 16:08:06 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>内塔尼亚胡关键部长米里·雷格夫因在加沙战争期间前往希腊度假而受到批评</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-23/ty-article/.premium/key-netanyahu-minister-miri-regev-blasted-for-vacationing-in-greece-amid-gaza-war/00000190-4594-d429-abfc-7dd63ef10000</link><description>以色列交通部长米里·雷格夫 (Miri Regev) 对希腊进行了私人访问，此前她于 2 月份前往印度和斯里兰卡度假，花费总计约 12 万美元，引发了众怒。</description><pubDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 15:35:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-23/ty-article/.premium/key-netanyahu-minister-miri-regev-blasted-for-vacationing-in-greece-amid-gaza-war/00000190-4594-d429-abfc-7dd63ef10000</guid></item><item><title>报告：真主党在贝鲁特民用机场储存伊朗武器和弹药</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-23/ty-article/report-hezbollah-storing-iranian-weapons-ammo-in-beiruts-civil-airport/00000190-4563-dafc-adb4-75eb04f60000</link><description>《每日电讯报》报道真主党在贝鲁特拉菲克·哈里里国际机场囤积伊朗武器后，以色列军队表示，如果真主党从该机场袭击平民，以色列军队“别无选择，只能做出回应”</description><pubDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 15:24:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-23/ty-article/report-hezbollah-storing-iranian-weapons-ammo-in-beiruts-civil-airport/00000190-4563-dafc-adb4-75eb04f60000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡任命前以色列国防军司令领导以色列北部的重建工作，以应对与真主党的冲突升级</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-23/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-appoints-former-idf-navy-chief-to-lead-north-israels-rehabilitation/00000190-455c-d768-adf8-4dfe5a310000</link><description>在与真主党发生数月冲突后，以色列北部的重建工作将由埃利泽·马罗姆领导，他在周日接受采访时表示，以色列人需要国际保证才能在黎巴嫩南部不发动军事行动的情况下返回北部</description><pubDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 14:50:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-23/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-appoints-former-idf-navy-chief-to-lead-north-israels-rehabilitation/00000190-455c-d768-adf8-4dfe5a310000</guid></item><item><title>警察暴行加剧，以色列警察在反政府抗议活动中推搡记者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-23/ty-article/.premium/police-officer-shoves-journalist-at-anti-govt-protest-amid-rising-police-brutality/00000190-4536-d91c-abba-ef367dae0000</link><description>在特拉维夫举行的一场反对总理内塔尼亚胡政府的抗议活动中，一名警察被看到暴力推搡一名明显是记者的妇女，以色列警方发表正式声明，对这一事件表示歉意</description><pubDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 14:28:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-23/ty-article/.premium/police-officer-shoves-journalist-at-anti-govt-protest-amid-rising-police-brutality/00000190-4536-d91c-abba-ef367dae0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡加大力度回应美国批评，称大部分弹药尚未抵达</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-23/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-doubles-down-on-u-s-criticism-says-most-munitions-yet-to-arrive/00000190-44e9-d429-abfc-7dfbe64e0000</link><description>总理为其公开批评美国的决定进行了辩护，称“从美国运往以色列的弹药大幅减少” ■ 国防部长加兰特将在华盛顿会见美国高级官员</description><pubDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 13:13:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-23/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-doubles-down-on-u-s-criticism-says-most-munitions-yet-to-arrive/00000190-44e9-d429-abfc-7dfbe64e0000</guid></item><item><title>宝贝，在以色列进行钻探：福音派石油公司在以色列启动了另一项勘探项目</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-23/ty-article/.premium/drill-baby-in-israel-evangelical-oil-company-launches-exploration-venture-in-israel/00000190-44e5-dafc-adb4-75ed4fab0000</link><description>锡安石油和天然气公司由一位美国基督徒创立，他表示希望促进以色列的能源独立，以帮助犹太人民</description><pubDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 12:30:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-23/ty-article/.premium/drill-baby-in-israel-evangelical-oil-company-launches-exploration-venture-in-israel/00000190-44e5-dafc-adb4-75ed4fab0000</guid></item><item><title>公设辩护人办公室：警察暴力践踏以色列人的人权，必须停止</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-23/ty-article/.premium/public-defenders-office-police-violence-tramples-human-rights-must-be-stopped/00000190-4478-da42-a1ba-7f7a5e330000</link><description>公设辩护人办公室的一名高级官员在对抗议活动的首次公开反应中表示，警察暴力是“对暴力警察不执法、对违法警察视而不见、宽大处理的结果”</description><pubDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 11:29:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-23/ty-article/.premium/public-defenders-office-police-violence-tramples-human-rights-must-be-stopped/00000190-4478-da42-a1ba-7f7a5e330000</guid></item><item><title>真主党瞄准以色列北部时，以色列国防军士兵被无人机重伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-23/ty-article-live/u-s-military-say-they-destroyed-three-houthi-vessels-in-red-sea/00000190-4301-d768-adf8-4fb3a7ac0000</link><description>真主党声称对向上加利利发射的无人机负责 ■ 哈马斯控制的加沙卫生部称，自战争爆发以来，有 37,598 名巴勒斯坦人在加沙地带丧生 ■ 内塔尼亚胡谈美国扣留武器运输：“主要群众留在后面” ■ 以色列国防军称一架无人机从加沙地带飞往以色列东部夜间被拦截 ■ 以色列士兵在加沙南部行动事故中丧生</description><pubDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 02:59:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-23/ty-article-live/u-s-military-say-they-destroyed-three-houthi-vessels-in-red-sea/00000190-4301-d768-adf8-4fb3a7ac0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军宣布，以色列士兵在加沙南部的行动事故中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-23/ty-article/israeli-soldier-killed-in-operational-accident-in-southern-gaza-idf-announces/00000190-4185-d8cb-a19d-49c7e91d0000</link><description>中士。一等兵马尔基亚·格罗斯 (Malkia Gross)，25 岁​​，来自约旦河西岸定居点苏西亚 (Susya)，在加沙南部被杀。格罗斯是一名数学老师，是苏西亚在战争中丧生的第四名士兵</description><pubDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 02:43:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-23/ty-article/israeli-soldier-killed-in-operational-accident-in-southern-gaza-idf-announces/00000190-4185-d8cb-a19d-49c7e91d0000</guid></item><item><title>卡塔尔向哈马斯施压，要求其放弃与以色列达成人质协议的要求</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-23/ty-article/.premium/qatar-pressuring-hamas-to-walk-back-its-demands-for-hostage-deal-with-israel/00000190-415e-d8cb-a19d-495ffe430000</link><description>停火和人质协议的谈判正在进行中，但以色列消息人士对进展感到悲观，称哈马斯目前对达成协议兴趣不大。卡塔尔正试图利用哈马斯放弃其最深远的要求，以期达成协议</description><pubDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 02:42:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-23/ty-article/.premium/qatar-pressuring-hamas-to-walk-back-its-demands-for-hostage-deal-with-israel/00000190-415e-d8cb-a19d-495ffe430000</guid></item><item><title>以色列卫生当局怀疑两名老年妇女死于西尼罗河病毒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/health/2024-06-22/ty-article/.premium/israeli-health-authorities-suspect-two-elderly-women-died-of-west-nile-virus/00000190-410a-d768-adf8-4dba33220000</link><description>导致妇女死亡的佩塔提克瓦医院正在等待实验室结果以确认死因 ■ 自 5 月以来，已有 19 名以色列人被诊断出感染该病毒，这是一个相对较高的数字 ■ 卫生部表示，今年早些时候出现了感染，可能是因为气候改变</description><pubDate>Sat, 22 Jun 2024 18:43:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/health/2024-06-22/ty-article/.premium/israeli-health-authorities-suspect-two-elderly-women-died-of-west-nile-virus/00000190-410a-d768-adf8-4dba33220000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战事，第 260 天：以色列国防军试图暗杀哈马斯官员；加沙人报告超过 40 人死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-22/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-260-idf-tries-to-assassinate-hamas-official-gazans-say-over-40-dead/00000190-40d1-d91c-abba-efd120ec0000</link><description>以色列国防军：试图在加沙城暗杀哈马斯高级官员；哈马斯：以色列两次袭击造成 42 人死亡 ■ 受伤的巴勒斯坦男子在约旦河西岸被捕后在以色列国防军车辆的引擎盖上被拍摄；以色列国防军：违反军队礼节的行为 ■ 60 岁的以色列人在约旦河西岸被巴勒斯坦人杀害 ■ 以色列国防军称其在黎巴嫩暗杀了哈马斯的主要特工 ■ 以下是战争 260 天后您需要了解的信息</description><pubDate>Sat, 22 Jun 2024 17:00:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-22/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-260-idf-tries-to-assassinate-hamas-official-gazans-say-over-40-dead/00000190-40d1-d91c-abba-efd120ec0000</guid></item><item><title>数万名以色列人抗议政府，要求人质协议；三人被捕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-22/ty-article/.premium/israelis-set-to-protest-netanyahus-coalition-demand-hostage-deal-across-country/00000190-409f-da42-a1ba-7fffc1660000</link><description>以色列主要城市和全国各地都在发生抗议活动。一名获释人质表示，她感到自己被政府“背叛”，而一名人质的兄弟则向内塔尼亚胡讲话，指责他“将政治生存置于亲人生命之上”</description><pubDate>Sat, 22 Jun 2024 16:14:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-22/ty-article/.premium/israelis-set-to-protest-netanyahus-coalition-demand-hostage-deal-across-country/00000190-409f-da42-a1ba-7fffc1660000</guid></item><item><title>视频显示受伤的巴勒斯坦人被绑在以色列国防军吉普车引擎盖上； 12 岁儿童在约旦河西岸被以色列国防军枪击身亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-22/ty-article/.premium/west-bank-video-shows-wounded-palestinian-on-idf-jeep-hood-12-year-old-dies-by-idf-fire/00000190-4039-d429-abfc-797bb1b20000</link><description>以色列军方表示，这段视频违反了其命令和程序；巴勒斯坦青少年在约旦河西岸村庄的冲突中受伤几天后死亡</description><pubDate>Sat, 22 Jun 2024 15:31:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-22/ty-article/.premium/west-bank-video-shows-wounded-palestinian-on-idf-jeep-hood-12-year-old-dies-by-idf-fire/00000190-4039-d429-abfc-797bb1b20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列试图暗杀加沙哈马斯高级指挥官；巴勒斯坦人报告超过 40 人死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-22/ty-article/.premium/israel-tries-to-assassinate-top-hamas-commander-in-gaza-palestinians-report-over-40-dead/00000190-401a-d5e8-a7f0-cd1f16fc0000</link><description>德国德新社报道称，哈马斯的目标官员是该组织行动部门负责人拉德·萨阿德，而以色列军方表示正在调查有关周五致命袭击的报道</description><pubDate>Sat, 22 Jun 2024 14:49:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-22/ty-article/.premium/israel-tries-to-assassinate-top-hamas-commander-in-gaza-palestinians-report-over-40-dead/00000190-401a-d5e8-a7f0-cd1f16fc0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列男子在约旦河西岸盖勒吉利亚被杀；国防部官员：可能是恐怖袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-22/ty-article/.premium/israeli-man-killed-in-west-bank-city-of-qalqilya-intent-of-attack-still-under-inve/00000190-3ec9-d8cb-a19d-7fcb967b0000</link><description>一名 60 岁的以色列男子在 Qalqilya 被枪杀，随后伤重不治。视频显示，巴勒斯坦医疗队正在救治这名男子，该男子后来在以色列拘留期间死亡</description><pubDate>Sat, 22 Jun 2024 08:13:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-22/ty-article/.premium/israeli-man-killed-in-west-bank-city-of-qalqilya-intent-of-attack-still-under-inve/00000190-3ec9-d8cb-a19d-7fcb967b0000</guid></item><item><title>美军称他们在红海摧毁了三艘胡塞武装船只</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-22/ty-article-live/25-gazans-reported-dead-in-rafah-strike-idf-first-probe-does-not-indicate-strike-there/00000190-3dea-d8cb-a19d-7debec640005</link><description>以色列各地数千人抗议政府和人质交易 ■ 以色列国防军试图在加沙城暗杀哈马斯官员；巴勒斯坦人报告超过 40 人死亡 ■ 60 岁的以色列人在约旦河西岸盖勒吉利耶被枪杀 ■ 以色列军队表示，他们在黎巴嫩深处的无人机袭击中暗杀了哈马斯的关键成员 ■ 反坦克导弹在以色列北部引发火灾；以色列国防军用炮火攻击发射场</description><pubDate>Sat, 22 Jun 2024 03:20:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-22/ty-article-live/25-gazans-reported-dead-in-rafah-strike-idf-first-probe-does-not-indicate-strike-there/00000190-3dea-d8cb-a19d-7debec640005</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡前雇员因欺凌、侵犯权利而获得 24 万美元赔偿</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-22/ty-article/.premium/former-netanyahu-employees-to-receive-240-000-for-bullying-rights-violations/00000190-3b89-da42-a1ba-7feb2c6e0000</link><description>两名维修工感觉自己像“现代奴隶”，其中一名经常违反程序被派往该家庭的私人住宅清洁游泳池。一名在该住所工作的厨师声称没有获得加班费</description><pubDate>Sat, 22 Jun 2024 03:07:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-22/ty-article/.premium/former-netanyahu-employees-to-receive-240-000-for-bullying-rights-violations/00000190-3b89-da42-a1ba-7feb2c6e0000</guid></item><item><title>去年，我决定放弃我的犹太身份。事情没有按计划进行</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-22/ty-article-opinion/.highlight/last-year-i-decided-to-turn-my-back-on-my-jewish-identity-it-didnt-go-as-planned/00000190-3ccf-da42-a1ba-7fefec8a0000</link><description>我对内塔尼亚胡-本-格维尔政府成立的最初反应是冷落我的犹太教，但我的尝试失败了——就像许多试图逃避民族身份但失败的人一样</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 22:23:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-22/ty-article-opinion/.highlight/last-year-i-decided-to-turn-my-back-on-my-jewish-identity-it-didnt-go-as-planned/00000190-3ccf-da42-a1ba-7fefec8a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的切尔克斯小社区在炮火中仍保留其烹饪传统</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/2024-06-22/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/israels-tiny-circassian-community-maintains-its-culinary-traditions-under-fire/00000190-3c99-d91c-abba-ff9980cf0000</link><description>在以色列北部的卡夫卡马，餐馆提供以传统切尔克斯奶酪为基础的美味佳肴。在其姊妹村雷哈尼亚 (Rehaniya)，美食旅游业因战争而被摧毁，当地企业正在艰难生存</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 21:58:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/2024-06-22/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/israels-tiny-circassian-community-maintains-its-culinary-traditions-under-fire/00000190-3c99-d91c-abba-ff9980cf0000</guid></item></channel></rss>